.TH FONTMGR "1" "December 2025" "fontmgr 202103310710-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
fontmgr \- Font ManaGeR for installing and managing fonts
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fontmgr
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] [\fI\,COMMAND\/\fR] [\fI\,FONTNAME\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B fontmgr
is a font management system for installing, updating, and managing fonts from preconfigured GitHub repositories. It provides a unified interface for managing programming fonts, nerd fonts, icon fonts, and other typefaces commonly used by developers and terminal users.
.PP
fontmgr supports installation from the fontmgr organization repositories on GitHub, automatic font cache updates, search functionality for discovering available fonts, and proper font version tracking. The tool is designed for developers, designers, and users who need consistent font installations across multiple systems.
.PP
All fonts are managed through Git repositories, making it easy to version control, update, and synchronize font installations across different machines.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B makecache
Update system font cache database after font changes. This command regenerates the font cache so newly installed fonts become available to applications.
.TP
.B list
List all fonts currently available in the fontmgr repository catalog
.TP
.B search \fI\,<term>\/\fR
Search for available fonts matching the specified term. Useful for finding fonts by name or style.
.TP
.B available
Show all available fonts from the GitHub repository. With authentication token configured, fetches complete list from GitHub API. Without token, shows predefined list.
.TP
.B install \fI\,<font>\/\fR
Install a font package from the preconfigured repository. Downloads the font files and installs them to the appropriate system location.
.TP
.B update \fI\,[font]\/\fR
Update font packages. If no font is specified, updates all installed fonts. If a specific font is provided, updates only that font.
.TP
.B remove \fI\,<font>\/\fR
Remove an installed font package and its files from the system
.TP
.B download \fI\,<font>\/\fR
Download or clone a font repository without installing. Useful for examining fonts or manual installation.
.TP
.B cron \fI\,[add|remove|run]\/\fR
Manage automatic font updates via cron job. Add schedules periodic updates, remove cancels scheduled updates, run executes update immediately.
.TP
.B version \fI\,<font>\/\fR
Display version information for an installed font package
